name: BetaPro Equal Weight Canadian REIT 2x Daily Bull ETF
longDescription: RITU seeks daily investment results, before fees, expenses, distributions, brokerage commissions and other transaction costs, that endeavour to correspond to two times (200 percent) the daily performance of the Solactive Equal Weight Canada REIT Index. RITU does not seek to achieve its stated investment objective over a period of time greater than one day.
